# Chrome Extension (Lucem)

- **Background**: MV3 service worker, no persistent page. Respect CSP in `src/manifest.json`.
- **Messaging**: validate sender/origin; `chrome.runtime.onMessage` in background only for `sender === webpage`.
- **Build**: webpack entries and `manifest.json` must stay aligned (bundle names, `web_accessible_resources`).
- **Platform boundary**: `src/pages/Background/`, `src/pages/Content/`, `src/api/messaging.js` are extension-only. Shared code in `src/api/`, `src/ui/`, `src/platform/` must not import `chrome.*` directly.
